OL,3,CDrunk cook died after fall from
OL,4,C'unsafe' ship gangway
OL,6,FA volunteer cook died after a falling
OL,7,Ffrom an 'unsafe' ship gangway in a
OL,8,FGloucestershire dock after a night of
OL,9,Fheavy drinking, a report has found.
OL,11,FMark Glover, 64, fell from the boat's
OL,12,Fgangway as he returned to the Pelican
OL,13,Fof London moored in Sharpness Docks,
OL,14,FGloucestershire.
OL,16,FThe Marine Accident Investigation
OL,17,FBranch (MAIB) report said he was above
OL,18,Fthe legal limit for duty on board a
OL,19,Fsailing ship when he fell and drowned
OL,20,Fon the evening of 2 October 2023.
