OL,3,CDrunk cook died after fall from
OL,4,C'unsafe' ship gangway
OL,6,FThe report found he drank at least
OL,7,Fnine double whiskies and ice before
OL,8,Freturning to the vessel.
OL,10,FHe was declared missing the next
OL,11,Fmorning, before police divers
OL,12,Frecovered his body on the afternoon of
OL,13,F3 October 2023.
OL,15,FThe key safety issues identified in
OL,16,Fthe report were:
OL,18,FThe drug and alcohol policy did not
OL,19,Fspecify parameters for crew returning
OL,20,Fon board from recreational time ashore.
