OL,6,FThe MAIB said drug and alcohol
OL,7,Fpolicies in place did not help crew
OL,8,Fmembers recognise the limits that
OL,9,Fapplied to crew returning from
OL,10,Frecreational time ashore.
OL,12,FThe report recommended the vessel's
OL,13,Fowners, Seas Your Future, to review
OL,14,Fpolicy and procedure for dealing with
OL,15,Fdrugs and or alcohol.
